            <title>[PIG-2214] InternalSortedBag two-arg constructor doesn&apos;t pass bagCount</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-2214</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The InternalSortedBag(int bagCount, Comparator&amp;lt;Tuple&amp;gt; comp) constructor doesn&apos;t properly pass bagCount to the three-arg constructor.&lt;/p&gt;

